The pMARS simulator has been successfully built from Debian source code without X11 dependencies and installed to `/usr/local/bin/pmars`.

**Summary of actions:**
1.  Enabled `deb-src` in `/etc/apt/sources.list.d/debian.sources`.
2.  Downloaded the `pmars` source package using `apt-get source`.
3.  Modified the `Makefile` in the source directory to:
